{"tid":309691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無綫反駁硬抽風波：如認為習講話不及《頭條新聞》重要 非專業新聞人","createTime":"2017-07-05T08:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T13:41:55.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c870a9b29ab743db5e49fe91ccfd88a2cc1217d","tid":309691,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170705/large/1499244073_b824.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170705%2Flarge%2F1499244073_b824.jpg&h=7bad9038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港電台諷刺時弊節目《頭條新聞》在6月30日晚6時原定於翡翠台播出，但無綫臨時聲稱有突發新聞，突將《頭條新聞》抽起延後播放，改為插播錄播的國家主席習近平與各界人士見面片段，其後並播放蘇民峰主持的本地遊節目《順峰順水》，被質疑因國家主席習近平訪港而自行「河蟹」。<br />\n<br />\n事隔6日，無綫今就有關指控回應傳媒的查詢，指習近平首次以國家主席身份訪港是重大新聞，主席發言特別受到關注，故無綫在互動新聞台即時報道外，亦安排在翡翠台直播或盡快錄播主席講話全文，故6月30日無綫決定整理有關pool片(聯合採訪片段)後於翡翠台盡快播出全文，並已即時通知香港電台負責人會抽調《頭條新聞》，建議安排在翌日下午在翡翠台同一時段或當晚凌晨12時30分在J5播出，經商討後港台亦同意選擇後者，而pool 片長度最終不足15分鐘，接著是《六點半新聞報道》，時間不足播放《頭條新聞》，只好以一些備用節目(《順峰順水》) 去填補剩餘時段，更直斥香港電台機構傳訊組總監伍曼儀，「如伍女士認為國家主席對香港各界人士講話全文不是新聞，或不及《頭條新聞》重要，乃罔顧事實，亦不是專業新聞或廣播人應有的說話」。<br />\n<br />\n無綫又同時炮轟需播放港台節目的安排，指無綫電視要播放港台節目是歷史遺留，至今已不合時宜，當年香港電台沒有自己的電視頻道，但自2014年1月香港電台開始數碼地面電視廣播，提供三條節目頻道，現時港台的覆蓋率和滲透率與無綫電視無異，「港台再無需要，亦沒有理由繼續免費佔用商營電視台寶貴高收視時段，去重複播放港台節目，令觀眾無選擇，亦影響商營電視台節目編排和調動的靈活性及機動性，理應盡快終止這不合時宜的安排」。<br />\n<br />\n但香港電台節目製作人員工會日前翻查資料發現，無綫在《頭條新聞》時段，插播國家主席習近平與各界人士見面片段，有關片段在其他電視台早在下午5時10分至5時15分已播出，無綫互動新聞台亦有播出。換言之，插播突發新聞只是舊聞。港台早前亦已表明沒有簽署接受節目調動的文件，更已致函無綫電視投訴並要求解釋，又對事件感到awfully displeased（非常不滿）。"},{"pid":"654d452b228c6ffd42e3c2bc9195c17143d08aa3","tid":309691,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:56:39.000Z","msg":"TVB樓屌<br />\n<br />\n講野咁撚似689既！"},{"pid":"e60819cc5c7f1c7cb40459fa8ecab6319b55096f","tid":309691,"uid":4537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:57:11.000Z","msg":"TVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港台好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0757ec5fc86e79d77206f896cc3b22571f506434","tid":309691,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:57:51.000Z","msg":"原來cctvb先係官媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eae92987acb35df9cce28129f53d047730b81df","tid":309691,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:58:19.000Z","msg":"TVB本身已經不合時宜<br />\n<br />\n睇新聞都睇靚樣大波報導員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c0ad4a231e3374664d36e4b482355c06e751a6","tid":309691,"uid":39379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:58:32.000Z","msg":"好撚惡咁喎"},{"pid":"7195bd5b1463a21479ea30fc6a56b7ca45ac6680","tid":309691,"uid":4964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:59:29.000Z","msg":"你又知頭條新聞入面冇習近平講話？<br />\n十足十九品芝麻官個太監一樣將老佛爺掛係口邊當武器"},{"pid":"6011f598723d8610ae8b0de818e54c36b26f1cdf","tid":309691,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:03:18.000Z","msg":"「港台再無需要，亦沒有理由繼續免費佔用商營電視台寶貴高收視時段，去重複播放港台節目，令觀眾無選擇，亦影響商營電視台節目編排和調動的靈活性及機動性，理應盡快終止這不合時宜的安排」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中學果時特登打開電視就係睇頭條新聞，其集咩節目都吸引唔到我開電視<br />\n係後尾我支持反蝗，同頭條新聞立場唔同<br />\n先冇再追"},{"pid":"abcc602fc0124b1b888c49aab40641ed73721b6f","tid":309691,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:05:33.000Z","msg":"如伍女士認為國家主席對香港各界人士講話全文不是新聞，或不及《頭條新聞》重要，乃罔顧事實，亦不是專業新聞或廣播人應有的說話」。<br />\n<br />\n食撚屎啦,支那人"},{"pid":"4049c52bc047a9240b7aaa165f63f9595bcffd92","tid":309691,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:06:20.000Z","msg":"交返個牌出o黎囉，播得咁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ab5ad0aac5548e005b94de333a5d46fbcd644c","tid":309691,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"又唔見CCTVB全程直播<br />\n講到咁大, 但係又播佢自己d垃圾節目都唔做直播"},{"pid":"1df68e3017b8258bbaf2bad808d17bf79615062b","tid":309691,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:07:25.000Z","msg":"唔播港台節目，又咪係播垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3fd658e46859d72c27240bf4d7e39452080b23a","tid":309691,"uid":70448,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>交返個牌出o黎囉，播得咁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支持無線交牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2dd2c04b24a6ef03daf76738fe6e813ed31132","tid":309691,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又唔見CCTVB全程直播<br />\n講到咁大, 但係又播佢自己d垃圾節目都唔做直播</blockquote><br />\n有接近成個鐘咁佢插入都唔插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9b6c53e93c51bfa80f43fdda197c0f3e93d282","tid":309691,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:08:13.000Z","msg":"同《中英聯合聲明》大同小異 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c500532a520d25f053133033c67e0c1360d3cd6c","tid":309691,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:09:58.000Z","msg":"Cctvb串得起<br />\n港台有撚人睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af0428984fab406186cc7a0cacd517cb903e6b67","tid":309691,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:13:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cctvb串得起<br />\n港台有撚人睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牌照有規定，而且之前有接近一個鐘比你插，即係卡通片重要過雜種啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d621fb3697a6f573b949b01b96025915b68b50c6","tid":309691,"uid":53278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cctvb串得起<br />\n港台有撚人睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實cctvb都冇人睇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大部分人都係開住黎做其他野"},{"pid":"ece440f7e62aa3db0644592a5b1ab0eae549ef27","tid":309691,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Cctvb串得起<br />\n港台有撚人睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牌照有規定，而且之前有接近一個鐘比你插，即係卡通片重要過雜種啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算唔計呢樣，播完雜種都可以繼續on schedule播返頭條最多冇左前半啫，一係你就插足半個鐘雜種，無喇喇走去播蘇民峰又有幾重要呀，唔通蘇民峰重要過雜種?"},{"pid":"346a68a1b633dc4f0dd7141025536f8350a8b6dd","tid":309691,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:29:56.000Z","msg":"即刻入黎負評先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c119096a3ca0801d64c67c4556ed04d13d964b1","tid":309691,"uid":76143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21afc2ea66601a9012b77afc5aaf73b75328898","tid":309691,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:31:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Cctvb串得起<br />\n港台有撚人睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牌照有規定，而且之前有接近一個鐘比你插，即係卡通片重要過雜種啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實真係串得起<br />\n<br />\n無香港人支持CCTVB呢隻巨獸邊得黎咁串"},{"pid":"49a7ceef5e698cbad0ce5312476287337563ff68","tid":309691,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:37:52.000Z","msg":"港台節目《頭條新聞》日前被無綫抽起，無綫回覆傳媒查詢時說，當日已即時通知港台會抽調節目，經商討後港台亦同意選擇當晚凌晨在J5台播出。<br />\n<br />\n港台機構傳訊組總監伍曼儀重申，港台沒有正式同意過無綫調動《頭條新聞》的做法，她說當時無綫在時間緊迫之下，提出要改於翌日播放；但港台指出，節目有時限性，一定要在即日播出，無綫則提出在當晚凌晨於另一頻道播出，這是無可奈何的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n伍曼儀又指，無綫當初表示要播放突發新聞，但結果播出的是國家主席習近平會見各界的預錄片段。伍曼儀承認及尊重主席訪港是重大新聞，但無綫當時所播出的片段並非突發新聞，其他電視台先前已經播放。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>小二，花生！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5871f542809b8b15e257ac1dbc884fd494c97c00","tid":309691,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:40:29.000Z","msg":"擦鞋擦到"},{"pid":"636ed9926f10921fc71865d843dedb51985b9c44","tid":309691,"uid":64155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:47:16.000Z","msg":"離晒譜"}]}